title: Schumer says Senate must pass funding bill with Ukraine aid quickly, 'hopefully tonight' - CNN

description: Senate Majority Leader Chuck Schumer said Thursday that Republicans and Democrats must work together to "quickly" pass a massive government funding bill with $13.6 billion in aid to Ukraine as soon as possible, "hopefully tonight."
